37#include <config.h>
38#include <krb5/krb5-types.h>
39
40#define VERSION_HIDDEN static HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE
41
42#include <krb5/roken.h>
43
44#include "version.h"
45
46void ROKEN_LIB_FUNCTION
47print_version(const char *progname)
48{
49 const char *package_list = heimdal_version;
50
51 if(progname == NULL)
52 progname = getprogname();
53
54 if(*package_list == '\0')
55 package_list = "no version information";
56 fprintf(stderr, "%s (%s)\n", progname, package_list);
57 fprintf(stderr, "Copyright 1995-2014 Kungliga Tekniska Högskolan\n");
58#ifdef PACKAGE_BUGREPORT
59 fprintf(stderr, "Send bug-reports to %s\n", PACKAGE_BUGREPORT);
60#endif
61}
